      "solution": "$a_2 = a_1 + 2(1) = 3 + 2 = 5$\n$a_3 = a_2 + 2(2) = 5 + 4 = 9$\n$a_4 = a_3 + 2(3) = 9 + 6 = 15$",
      "solTex": "$a_4 = 15$",
