      "solution": "$x^3 - 8 = (x - 2)(x^2 + 2x + 4)$이므로\n$\\displaystyle\\lim_{x \\to 2} \\dfrac{(x-2)(x^2+2x+4)}{x-2} = \\lim_{x \\to 2}(x^2+2x+4)$\n$= 4 + 4 + 4 = 12$",
